To the geniuses at Netflix who took up this project: Thank you thank you thank you. You have vision. You have courage. Keep going. Show them how to do it.

To the writers and creatives and actors of OTNB: Thank you thank you thank you. For your 

1. courage - to tackle the topic of female prisons, female prisoners, realistic presentation of lesbianism, realistic presentation of female bodies, realistic presentation of the female species as fully developed human beings capable of extreme goodness and evil.

2. imagination - to create humanity and sensitivity where it is the hardest to find or maintain.

3. intelligence - to know the priority, to make the right choices, to know what to highlight and what to sacrifice. 

Don't let the naysayers and haters bring you down. You're doing great work with meaning and deep love, and may good karma and power be with you all.